{
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [
    { "asDropdown": false, "icon": "external link", "includeVars": true, "keepTime": true, "tags": [], "targetBlank": false, "title": "Stack", "type": "link", "url": "/d/tracelogkit_stack" },
    { "asDropdown": false, "icon": "external link", "includeVars": true, "keepTime": true, "tags": [], "targetBlank": false, "title": "Business Metrics", "type": "link", "url": "/d/tracelogkit_business_metrics" },
    { "asDropdown": false, "icon": "external link", "includeVars": true, "keepTime": true, "tags": [], "targetBlank": false, "title": "Logs", "type": "link", "url": "/d/tracelogkit_logs" }
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "description": "**流程**：从 Logs 点击 task_id 进入，或手动输入 task_id。\n\n1. **Trace 列表**：该任务的所有执行（首次+重试），按时间排序\n2. **点击 traceID**：在下方展示该 trace 的链路可视化（waterfall）\n3. **在 waterfall 中点击 span**：可反查该 span 的 Loki 日志（tracesToLogs）\n4. **重试分析**：多条 trace = 多次执行，对比各次可判断重试次数、是否成功、失败原因",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": { "content": "", "mode": "markdown" },
      "title": "使用说明",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tracelogkit-tempo" },
      "description": "输入 task_id 查询该任务的所有 trace（首次执行、重试1、重试2…）。点击 traceID 列在下方展示链路。",
      "gridPos": { "h": 14, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "id": 2,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "traceID" },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "links",
                "value": [
                  { "title": "查看链路", "url": "/d/tracelogkit_traces?var-task_id=$task_id&var-trace_id=${__value.raw}" }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": { "countRows": false, "fields": "", "reducer": ["sum"], "show": false },
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [{ "desc": true, "displayName": "Start time" }]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tracelogkit-tempo" },
          "queryType": "traceqlSearch",
          "refId": "A",
          "query": "{ span.task_id = \"$task_id\" }",
          "limit": 50
        }
      ],
      "title": "Trace 列表（按 task_id）",
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "merge", "options": {} },
        { "id": "organize", "options": { "excludeByName": { "nested": true }, "indexByName": {}, "renameByName": { "traceID": "traceID", "traceDuration": "Duration", "startTime": "Start time" } } }
      ],
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tracelogkit-tempo" },
      "description": "展示选中 trace 的链路可视化。从上方表格点击 traceID 传入，或手动输入 trace_id。",
      "gridPos": { "h": 20, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {},
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tracelogkit-tempo" },
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "refId": "A",
          "query": "${trace_id}"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Trace 时间线（Waterfall）",
      "type": "traces"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "5s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "style": "dark",
  "tags": ["tracelogkit", "traces", "tempo"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      { "name": "task_id", "label": "task_id", "type": "textbox", "query": "", "hide": 0, "current": { "selected": false, "text": "", "value": "" } },
      { "name": "trace_id", "label": "trace_id", "type": "textbox", "query": "", "hide": 0, "current": { "selected": false, "text": "", "value": "" } }
    ]
  },
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "Traces",
  "uid": "tracelogkit_traces",
  "version": 1
}
